p: King County on the 8th day of January A. D. 1878 at ten o clock am the foreseen of that day to do and recieve where shall they and then be considered concerning the aid John W. Gardain. And have you then and there this writ. Witness the Hon. Joseph R. Lewis Chief justice of the 3rd Judicial District therein this 2nd day of January A.D. 1879. Alter my and the seal of District Cour the day and your last writngs Clerk Deputy
